SHIGELLA - CANADA (MONTREAL): CORRECTION
========================================
[see: Shigella conney - Canada (Montreal) - posted today]
Date: Mon, 12 May 1997 18:34:24 +0100
From: Burnens Andre <burnens@vbi.unibe.ch>

The bacterium you refer to most certainly is Shigella sonnei (named after
Carl Sonne).
